Source code for the post
http://matcross.wordpress.com/2012/10/30/in-at-the-dep-end/
about Fortran module-dependency analysis:

generate_fortran.py
  generates the input Fortran source files that demonstrate a complex
  tree of module dependencies;
Makefile
  the GNU makefile for building the Fortran source.
  Analysis of module dependencies happens automatically.  
